data.description: Cheerfully Vibrant and Updated Home in Newark! Picturesquely tucked away in an idyllic small town, this 3+BR/2BA, 1,815sqft residence immediately charms with beautiful new siding, a canary yellow front door, an inviting covered front porch, and a neatly landscaped 0.26-acre lot. Marvelously maintained and perfectly kept, the interior further captivates with gleaming hardwood flooring, an attractive color scheme, abundant natural light, rustic wood trim, and a spacious living room. Holiday gatherings and cozy morning meals are a cinch in the updated kitchen, which includes stainless-steel appliances, granite countertops,large pantry,  wood cabinetry, gas stove, built-in microwave, dishwasher, stylish tile backsplash, French door refrigerator, and an adjoining dining area. Three upper-level bedrooms are generously sized. Upper-level full bathroom with a shower/tub combo and a storage vanity. As a fabulous bonus, the lower-level offers an enormous flex room/potential 4th bedroom and a full bathroom. Enjoy the entertainment-ready outdoor space. Boasting a shaded oversized concrete patio, the backyard also has tons of greenspace for gardening and playing games. Other features: oversized detached 2.5 car garage, New Furnace and AC w/transferable warranty, laundry room, quick 29-mile drive to Downtown Naperville or 60-miles to Downtown Chicago, close to restaurants, schools, and shopping, and more! Call now to schedule your showing!--
